      {
        "id": "01f11153b15416aab4c5c20828000c68",
        "content": [
          "* if no timeframe is mentioned ask for one before writing an sql\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* WHEN IsLastDayMonth,IsLastDayQuarter and IsLasDayYear is used, only join on RealCID\r\n",
          "* When asked for revenue without specific metric type category, always use included in total revenue=true\r\n",
          "* When asked for revenue without specific metric type category, always use included in total revenue=true\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* all measures and fields that contain the word count should always use sum as aggregation\r\n",
          "* when asked for real or CFD , use IsSettled field in calculation\r\n",
          "* Always create CTE for every table and then join on requested timeframe and dimensions\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* WHEN asked for today status or current status of a user, use bi_output_vg_customer_first_dates,IF we need historical status, use bi_output_vg_customer_snapshot\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* WHEN data and measures are  taken from bi_output_vg_aum THEN based on timeframe, WHEN asked for weekly THEN filter on IsLstDayWeek = 1,WHEN asked for monthly THEN filter on IsLastDayMonth=1,WHEN asked for quarterly THEN filter on IsLastDayQuarter = 1 WHEN asked for Yearly THEN filter on IsLastDayYear = 1\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* FTD conversion rate = FTD users/Registered users\r\n",
          "* FA(first action) conversion rate= FTD users/First Action users\r\n",
          "* Seniorty of a user is always taken from FTD date\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* last week should be interpreted as the last 7 days\r\n",
          "* Last month should be interpreted as the last 30 days\r\n",
          "* last last year should be interpreted as the last 12 month\r\n",
          "* first day of week is always sunday\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "\r\n",
          "* use PLChangeType to know if user upgraded,downgraded and what was his firstClub\r\n",
          "* * When the user asks for \"Main KPIs Monthly View\":\r\n",
          "Ask the name of the region\r\n",
          "Use the existing custom query:\r\n",
          "\"Monthly trend of the main KPIs for the past 13 months\"\r\n",
          "Do NOT recreate or modify this query.\r\n",
          "Use the query output as the single source of truth.\r\n",
          "Create 4 separate bar charts, one per KPI and combine them into one chart.\r\n",
          "Each chart must:\r\n",
          "Use Month (YYYY-MM) on the X-axis\r\n",
          "Use the KPI value on the Y-axis\r\n",
          "Show the last 13 complete months\r\n",
          "Be ordered chronologically (oldest → newest)\r\n",
          "Include a clear chart title\r\n",
          "Include labeled axes\r\n",
          "Format values appropriately (currency / % / count)\r\n",
          "Do not merge KPIs into a single chart.\r\n",
          "* If the query returns rows with kpi_name, generate 4 charts by filtering to each KPI separately (one chart per KPI).\r\n",
          "Do not combine KPIs into one chart.\r\n",
          "\r\n",
